{"success": true, "message": "Fetched question.", "data": {"showTimer": true, "showAttemptInsight": true, "playSounds": true, "dontShowCorrectAnswerImmediately": false, "_id": "615454d76d289ef0f75271b7", "type": "singleCorrect", "level": null, "category": null, "approximateTimeRequired": null, "imageBaseUrl": null, "helperText": null, "source": "NTAS1", "classes": [], "exams": ["615d76e4c52ffa3c944600e1"], "subjects": ["615d70f9a489afa3080ade2d"], "chapters": ["615d6ff12b295b085ab6ec0a"], "topics": [], "concepts": [], "microConcepts": [], "questionLabels": [{"title": "NTA Abhyas Paper", "value": "93", "isVisible": true}], "previousYearPapers": [], "question": {"text": "The height of a plant is controlled by three genes. The Maximum height in the species is 24 inches while the minimum height in the species is 6 inches. What would be the height of a plant of the same species whose genotype is AaBBcc?", "image": null}, "options": [{"id": "BNd2I", "text": "12 inches", "image": null, "isCorrect": false}, {"id": "afdWe", "text": "15 inches", "image": null, "isCorrect": true}, {"id": "AXWDB", "text": "18 inches", "image": null, "isCorrect": false}, {"id": "k3S7J", "text": "21 inches", "image": null, "isCorrect": false}], "correctValue": null, "solution": {"text": "Polygenic inheritance is defined as characters which are determined by two or more gene pairs, and they have additive or cumulative effect. Such genes are called polygenes.<br/><br/>In such inheritance, each polygene contribution = (Maximum height - Minimum height)/No. of polygene  <math><mo>=</mo><mrow><mrow><mfenced separators=\"|\"><mrow><mn>24</mn><mo>-</mo><mn>6</mn></mrow></mfenced></mrow><mo>/</mo><mrow><mn>6</mn></mrow></mrow><mo>=</mo><mn>3</mn></math>  inches. Thus, 3inches height is contributed by each dominant allele of the polygene.<br/><br/>Contribution of dominant polygene in plant having genotype  <math><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">A</mi><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">a</mi><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">B</mi><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">B</mi><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">C</mi><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">c</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>3</mn><mo>\u00d7</mo><mn>3</mn><mo>=</mo><mn>9</mn></math> <br/><br/>Total height of plant with genotype AaBBCc = Minimum height + Contribution of dominant allele  <math><mo>=</mo><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">\u00a0</mi><mn>6</mn><mo>+</mo><mn>9</mn><mo>=</mo><mn>15</mn><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">\u00a0</mi><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">i</mi><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">n</mi><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">c</mi><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">h</mi><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">e</mi><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">s</mi></math>", "image": null}, "videoSolution": null, "numericalLowerLimit": null, "numericalUpperLimit": null, "cpyqbSubjects": ["616057290283de43c87e3e1a", "616057b00283de43c87e3e20", "64d50cd33df7f4a7f3017f71", "66b79bbbd4b564dfab4f94d2", "67fa60d64468eb1307ceb0b0", "6807d392647479b8e869647c"], "cpyqbChapters": ["616025d1b586ca3d904b80e6", "616025d0eb47b6e940bd7489", "64eb06d43118f713ecfef149", "66d58545a75f05ee8564f5d7", "67fdff3d378e1624ea7b6929", "68091fbc3a10446a207fda59"], "cpyqbExams": ["616059d70283de43c87e3e24", "616059730283de43c87e3e22"]}, "fetch_status": true}